title: [Grawood Farmstead, Meadow]
description: A wild rose vine has staked its claim on a portion of the fence here, trailing down and around the wood, brightening the lackluster rails with flowers of deep crimson.  The fragrance of the blossoms fills the air, sweet and heady, with the slightest hint of spice
room.location: Grawood Farmstead outside of River's Rest
